. MEMORY1/FIX - 08/27/90 - Patch to LS-DOS 6.3.1 SYS6/SYS
. Patch cleans up video screen when data goes to 2nd screen.
. Apply via DO FIX631G (D=n) ... See FIX631G/JCL
D04,63=18;F04,63=17
D04,6E=7F;F04,6E=0C
D04,DB=15;F04,DB=0F
D04,F2=CD 9C 27 C3 6A 27
F04,F2="No mem"
D04,F8="No memory"
F04,F8="ory space"
. Eop
